  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 420" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Capacité à Identifier les Causes d'un Événement Futur — Formulation Standard vs. Rétrospective Prospective</text>
    <text x="20" y="53" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Indice de capacité d'identification des causes (formulation standard = 100) · Environ 30 % plus élevé en rétrospective prospective</text>
    <line x1="90" y1="350" x2="660" y2="350" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="80" x2="90" y2="350" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="260" x2="660" y2="260" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="170" x2="660" y2="170" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="80" x2="660" y2="80" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
    <text x="80" y="354" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">0</text>
    <text x="80" y="264" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">50</text>
    <text x="80" y="174" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">100</text>
    <text x="80" y="84" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">150</text>
    <rect x="180" y="170" width="140" height="180" fill="#71717a" opacity="0.6" rx="3"/>
    <rect x="420" y="116" width="140" height="234" fill="#4ade80" rx="3"/>
    <text x="250" y="160" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">100</text>
    <text x="490" y="106" fill="#0a0a0a" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">≈130</text>
    <text x="250" y="368" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Formulation Standard</text>
    <text x="250" y="384" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">(« pourquoi cela pourrait arriver ? »)</text>
    <text x="490" y="368" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Rétrospective Prospective</text>
    <text x="490" y="384" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">(« c'est déjà arrivé »)</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="fr" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">* Résumé des résultats expérimentaux de Mitchell, Russo &amp; Pennington (1989). Lorsque les participants devaient supposer qu'un événement futur « s'était déjà produit » puis en expliquer les raisons, leur capacité à identifier les causes était environ 30 % plus élevée que sous la formulation standard.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pt">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 420" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Capacidade de Identificar Causas de um Evento Futuro — Formulação Padrão vs. Retrospectiva Prospectiva</text>
    <text x="20" y="53" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Índice de capacidade de identificação de causas (formulação padrão = 100) · Cerca de 30% mais alto na retrospectiva prospectiva</text>
    <line x1="90" y1="350" x2="660" y2="350" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="80" x2="90" y2="350" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="260" x2="660" y2="260" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="170" x2="660" y2="170" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="80" x2="660" y2="80" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
    <text x="80" y="354" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">0</text>
    <text x="80" y="264" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">50</text>
    <text x="80" y="174" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">100</text>
    <text x="80" y="84" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">150</text>
    <rect x="180" y="170" width="140" height="180" fill="#71717a" opacity="0.6" rx="3"/>
    <rect x="420" y="116" width="140" height="234" fill="#4ade80" rx="3"/>
    <text x="250" y="160" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">100</text>
    <text x="490" y="106" fill="#0a0a0a" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">≈130</text>
    <text x="250" y="368" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Formulação Padrão</text>
    <text x="250" y="384" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">("por que poderia acontecer?")</text>
    <text x="490" y="368" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Retrospectiva Prospectiva</text>
    <text x="490" y="384" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">("já aconteceu")</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="pt" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">* Resumo dos resultados experimentais de Mitchell, Russo &amp; Pennington (1989). Quando os participantes deviam assumir que um evento futuro "já havia acontecido" e depois explicar o porquê, sua capacidade de identificar causas foi cerca de 30% maior do que sob a formulação padrão.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="tr">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 420" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Gelecekteki Bir Olayın Nedenlerini Belirleme Yeteneği — Standart Soru vs. İleriye Dönük Geriye Bakış</text>
    <text x="20" y="53" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Neden belirleme yeteneği endeksi (standart soru = 100) · İleriye dönük geriye bakışta yaklaşık %30 daha yüksek</text>
    <line x1="90" y1="350" x2="660" y2="350" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="80" x2="90" y2="350" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="260" x2="660" y2="260" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="170" x2="660" y2="170" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="80" x2="660" y2="80" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
    <text x="80" y="354" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">0</text>
    <text x="80" y="264" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">50</text>
    <text x="80" y="174" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">100</text>
    <text x="80" y="84" fill="#71717a" font-size="13" text-anchor="end" font-family="sans-serif">150</text>
    <rect x="180" y="170" width="140" height="180" fill="#71717a" opacity="0.6" rx="3"/>
    <rect x="420" y="116" width="140" height="234" fill="#4ade80" rx="3"/>
    <text x="250" y="160" fill="#e4e4e7" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">100</text>
    <text x="490" y="106" fill="#0a0a0a" font-size="16" text-anchor="middle" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">≈130</text>
    <text x="250" y="368" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">Standart Soru</text>
    <text x="250" y="384" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">("neden olabilir?")</text>
    <text x="490" y="368" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">İleriye Dönük Geriye Bakış</text>
    <text x="490" y="384" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" text-anchor="middle" font-family="sans-serif">("zaten oldu")</text>
  </svg>
  <p class="tr" style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;margin-top:-10px">* Mitchell, Russo &amp; Pennington (1989) deneysel sonuçlarının özeti. Katılımcılardan gelecekteki bir olayın "zaten gerçekleştiğini" varsaymaları ve ardından nedenini açıklamaları istendiğinde, neden belirleme yetenekleri standart soru biçimine göre yaklaşık %30 daha yüksek çıktı.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="vi">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 700 420" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
    <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="15" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Khả Năng Xác Định Nguyên Nhân Của Một Sự Kiện Tương Lai — Cách Hỏi Tiêu Chuẩn vs. Hồi Tưởng Có Chủ Đích</text>
    <text x="20" y="53" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13" font-family="sans-serif">Chỉ số khả năng xác định nguyên nhân (cách hỏi tiêu chuẩn = 100) · Cao hơn khoảng 30% trong điều kiện hồi tưởng có chủ đích</text>
    <line x1="90" y1="350" x2="660" y2="350" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="80" x2="90" y2="350" stroke="#3f3f46" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="90" y1="260" x2="660" y2="260" stroke="#27272a" stroke-dasharray="4,4" stroke-width="1"/>
